Summarization Project
Extracts text from PDF files, summarizes it using a pre-trained BART model, and saves the summary as a new PDF for efficient content comprehension.
 
Features  
Text Extraction: Extract text from PDF files using `PyMuPDF`.  
Summarization: Generate concise summaries using the `facebook/bart-large-cnn` model from Hugging Face.  
Save Summary: Save the summarized content as a new PDF. 

Usage
Place Your PDF: Ensure the PDF file is in the working directory or specify the full path.
Update the File Path: Replace the pdf_file_path variable in the script with the path to your PDF.
Run the Script: Execute the script to extract, summarize, and save the output.

Acknowledgements
Hugging Face Transformers for the pre-trained BART model.
PyMuPDF library for efficient PDF text extraction.

Example Output
Generated Summary:
A concise summary of the PDF content.
